lagship lounges are being refurbished • early boarding • first class amenity kit • turndown service with pajamas • a pair of bose quietcomfort acoustic noise canceling headsets to use during flight • inflight wine tasting • premium alcoholic beverages and wine selections including predeparture champagne service • chefinspired dining options • access to the premium cabin walkup bar which features assorted snacks and beverages throughout the duration of the flight international business classedit sky club boarding pass • airbus a fully lieflat cirrus seats manufactured by zodiac seats france and designed by jpa design with direct aisle access in a  reverse herringbone configuration seat length  inches – cm equipped with a  inch  cm touchscreen monitor one universal ac power outlet and usb ports • boeing er fully lieflat cirrus seats manufactured by zodiac seats uk designed by jpa design and licensed from cathay pacific with direct aisle access in a  reverse herringbone configuration seat length  inches – cm equipped with a   cm inch touchscreen monitor one universal ac power outlet and usb ports • boeing  fully lieflat seats manufactured by zodiac seats france and designed for american airlines with direct aisle access in a  reverse herringbone configuration with frontfacing and rearfacing seats seat length  inches cm equipped with a inch  cm touchscreen monitor and touchscreen handset two universal ac power outlets and usb ports • boeing er postretrofit version  fully lieflat seats manufactured by zodiac seats france designed for american airlines with direct aisle access in a  reverse herringbone configuration with frontfacing and rearfacing seats seat length  inches cm equipped with a inch  cm touchscreen monitor and touchscreen handset two universal ac power outlets and usb ports • boeing er postretrofit version  fully lieflat super diamond seats manufactured by be aerospace and designed for american airlines with direct aisle access in a  reverse herringbone conf